flowchart LR
    A["Pengguna mengirim\npesan chat"] --> B["POST /api/chat"]
    B --> C["Generate Query\nEmbedding"]
    C --> D{"Mode Retrieval?"}
    D -->|Hybrid| E["Vector Search +\nBM25 (RRF)"]
    D -->|Vector Only| F["Cosine Similarity\npgvector"]
    E --> G{"Confidence\nClassification"}
    F --> G
    G -->|High >= 0.55| H["Build Context\n(max 3000 tokens)"]
    G -->|Medium >= 0.40| H
    G -->|Low >= 0.30| H2["Tambahkan prefix\n'Informasi terbatas...'"]
    G -->|Refuse < 0.30| I["Penolakan sopan\n'Maaf, saya tidak...'"]
    H2 --> H
    H --> J["Konstruksi System Prompt\n(berdasarkan mode widget)"]
    J --> K["LLM Generate\nStreaming Response"]
    K --> L["Simpan response\n+ sources ke DB"]
    L --> M["Return response\n+ X-Sources header"]
    I --> M2["Return refusal\nmessage"]

    style A fill:#cd8c68,color:#fff
    style M fill:#5baaad,color:#fff
    style I fill:#e74c3c,color:#fff
    style M2 fill:#e74c3c,color:#fff